divs: Sighting DetailsThis was not a sighting but what was caught on a photo we took. We stopped to take two pictures of a spectacular sunset..two days later the photos were uploaded and one the two photos was saved as a new wall paper for my computer. I saw a spot on what I thought was the monitor thinking it was a speck of dust. With further zoom-ins it was clear that it wasn't a pixel problem or dust on the lens. The most puzzling of the two photos is of the black orb. The other figure is up and to the right of a bird in flight. Both are puzzling and we would like a good explanation.
